      "seed": 1711647932,
      "version": 537,
      "versionNonce": 468284092,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780743523247,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "System Flow\n\n1. User taps emoji on screen\n2. Emoji service receives the api request\n3. Do some validation and publish to Kafka topic emoji-events\n4. Return 200 status to client, without making sure downstream processing\n5. Stream Processor aggregates result over a window = 1 sec\n6. Publish aggregates to Kafka topic : emoji-aggregates\n7. Fanout Service broadcasts to client using MQTT clusters",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "System Flow\n\n1. User taps emoji on screen\n2. Emoji service receives the api request\n3. Do some validation and publish to Kafka topic emoji-events\n4. Return 200 status to client, without making sure downstream processing\n5. Stream Processor aggregates result over a window = 1 sec\n6. Publish aggregates to Kafka topic : emoji-aggregates\n7. Fanout Service broadcasts to client using MQTT clusters",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
