      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1780938274490,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Contactless digital payment where payment is done by scanning a QR code\nat POS from mobile app and money is transferred from buyer's wallet\nto seller's wallet or account.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Contactless digital payment where payment is done by scanning a QR code\nat POS from mobile app and money is transferred from buyer's wallet\nto seller's wallet or account.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "8NQrENvL6XVTstMpgd6la",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 328.1051653124107,
      "y": 395.15979740476456,
      "width": 657.0794677734375,
      "height": 450,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b2j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 138952892,
      "version": 851,
      "versionNonce": 1160884540,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781109599354,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n\n- users should be able to make payments by scanning QR code\n- users can view payment status and history\n---------------------------\n- merchants should be able to generate QR code - static / dynamic\n- merchants can view payment status, and refund them\n\n\n\nNon-functional requirements\n\n- Low latency QR lookups < 500ms\n- Payment confirmation < 2 sec\n- Highly consistent system, no duplicate payments(idempotency)\n- Auditability\n- Scale to 1M/qps\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n\n- users should be able to make payments by scanning QR code\n- users can view payment status and history\n---------------------------\n- merchants should be able to generate QR code - static / dynamic\n- merchants can view payment status, and refund them\n\n\n\nNon-functional requirements\n\n- Low latency QR lookups < 500ms\n- Payment confirmation < 2 sec\n- Highly consistent system, no duplicate payments(idempotency)\n- Auditability\n- Scale to 1M/qps\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
